# Ralph reviewer: one senior-review pass at :13 and :43 past every hour.
# Install with:  crontab -e   (paste the line below)
# Appends to ~/review-board.log. SHADOW mode by default (no auto-merge).
13,43 * * * * /home/div/.local/bin/review-board

# Ralph worker: autonomous pickup, SCOPED TO REP-SHEET + SKILLS (engineer-board's jq filter).
# Runs at :00 and :30. Appends to ~/engineer-board.log. Every Ready-for-Agent or
# Changes-Requested card on either becomes a live trigger. Widen by relaxing the jq
# filter (or drop it entirely to iterate every repo, like review-board).
0,30 * * * * /home/div/.local/bin/engineer-board

# Per-profile Linear token refresh (ENG-133).
# Iterates every `hermes-<repo>` wrapper on PATH and refreshes each profile's
# Linear MCP token. Replaces the single-profile refresh cron entry once the
# per-repo profiles exist on the box; until then the wrapper logs "skipped"
# for each missing profile and exits 0 (steady state, not a failure).
0 */6 * * * /home/div/.local/bin/refresh-profile-tokens.sh >> /home/div/linear-refresh.log 2>&1